\c 31
\s Ukubizwa kukaBhezaleli loOholiyaba
\p
\v 1 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasikhuluma kuMozisi yathi:
\v 2 Bona, ngibizile ngebizo uBhezaleli indodana kaUri indodana kaHuri\x + 35.30; 36.1. 1 Lan. 2.20.\x* owesizwe sakoJuda\x + 17.10,12.\x*;
\v 3 ngimgcwalisile ngoMoya kaNkulunkulu, ekuhlakanipheni lekuqedisiseni lelwazini lakuyo yonke imisebenzi yobungcitshi\x + 35.31. 1 Kho. 7.14.\x*,
\v 4 ukuthi aqambe imisebenzi yobungcitshi, asebenze ngegolide langesiliva langethusi,
\v 5 ekubazeni amatshe ukuwafaka, lekubazeni izigodo, ukwenza yonke imisebenzi yobungcitshi.
\v 6 Mina-ke, khangela, nginike uOholiyaba indodana kaAhisamaki\x + 35.34.\x* owesizwe sakoDani kanye laye; lenhliziyweni yakhe wonke ohlakaniphileyo ngenhliziyo ngifake inhlakanipho\x + 28.3.\x*, ukuthi benze konke engikulaye khona,
\v 7 ithente lenhlangano\x + 36.8-38.\x*, lomtshokotsho wobufakazi\x + 37.1-5.\x*, lesihlalo somusa esiphezu kwawo\x + 37.6-9.\x*, lempahla yonke yethente,
\v 8 letafula lezitsha zalo\x + 37.10-16.\x*, loluthi lwesibane olucwengekileyo\x + 37.17-24.\x* lezitsha zalo zonke, lelathi lempepha\x + 37.25-28.\x*,
\v 9 lelathi lomnikelo wokutshiswa\x + 38.1-7.\x* lezitsha zalo zonke, lenditshi yokugezela lonyawo lwayo\x + 38.8.\x*,
\v 10 lezembatho ezifekethisiweyo, lezembatho ezingcwele zikaAroni umpristi, lezembatho zamadodana akhe, ukusebenza njengabapristi\x + 35.19; 39.1,41. Nani. 4.5,6.\x*,
\v 11 lamafutha okugcoba\x + 30.25,31; 37.29.\x*, lempepha emnandi yendawo engcwele\x + 30.7,34.\x*; benze njengakho konke engikulaye khona.
\s Ukugcinwa kwamasabatha
\p
\v 12 IN\nd kosi\nd* yasikhuluma kuMozisi isithi:
\v 13 Wena-ke, tshela abantwana bakoIsrayeli uthi: Isibili lizagcina amasabatha ami\x + 20.8. 23.12. 35.2. Levi 19.3,30. 26.2. Dute. 5.12. Jer. 17.22. Hez. 20.12,20. 44.24.\x*; ngoba lokhu kuyisibonakaliso phakathi kwami lani ezizukulwaneni zenu, ukwazi ukuthi ngiyiN\nd kosi\nd* elingcwelisayo.
\v 14 Ngakho gcinani isabatha, ngoba lingcwele kini; olonayo uzabulawa lokubulawa; ngoba wonke owenza umsebenzi ngalo, lowomphefumulo uzaqunywa usuke ebantwini bawo\x + 35.2. Nani 15.35.\x*.
\v 15 Insuku eziyisithupha kwenziwe umsebenzi\x + 20.9.\x*, kodwa ngosuku lwesikhombisa kulisabatha lokuphumula\x + Gen. 2.2; Eks. 16.23; 20.10.\x*, lingcwele eN\nd kosi\nd*ni; wonke owenza umsebenzi ngesabatha uzabulawa lokubulawa.
\v 16 Ngakho abantwana bakoIsrayeli bazagcina isabatha, balilondoloze isabatha ezizukulwaneni zabo, libe yisivumelwano esilaphakade.
\v 17 Liyisibonakaliso phakathi kwami labantwana bakoIsrayeli kuze kube nini lanini\x + 31.13. Hez. 20.12,20.\x*; ngoba ngensuku eziyisithupha iN\nd kosi\nd* yenza amazulu lomhlaba\x + Gen. 1.31; 2.2.\x*, kodwa ngosuku lwesikhombisa yaphumula, yavuselelwa.
\p
\v 18 Wasemnika uMozisi, eseqedile ukukhuluma laye entabeni yeSinayi, izibhebhe ezimbili zobufakazi, izibhebhe zamatshe, zibhalwe ngomunwe kaNkulunkulu\x + 24.12. 32.15,16. Dute. 4.13. 5.22. 9.10,11. 2 Kor. 3.3.\x*.
